<h2 class="bold font-l">The Great Muppet Caper</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The climax of the film, has the Muppets playing keep away with the Baseball Diamond, from Nicky and his gang, which soon turns into a full on baseball game, with Scooter selling popcorn, the rats acting as fans and Louis Kazager doing commentary. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
